graph LR
    VLLM["vLLM ROCm<br/>Container Image"]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    VLLM -->|"base image<br/>v3.2.1"| AIPCC["AIPCC Base Image<br/>rhaiis/vllm-rocm-rhel9"]
